  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/items/inventory/lantern.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can expend 1 point of mental focus to heal a living creature with a touch. The creature is healed an amount of damage equal to 1d8 + your occultist level.</p>\n<p>For every 4 occultist levels you possess beyond 3rd, the creature is healed an additional 1d8 points of damage, to a maximum of 5d8+19 at 19th level. This has no effect on undead creatures.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 3rd level to select this focus power.</p>"
    },
